##  (which might be a polynomial ring).
##  <Example><![CDATA[
##  gap> Resultant(x^4+y,y^4+x,1);
##  y^16+y
##  gap> Resultant(x^4+y,y^4+x,2);
##  x^16+x
##  ]]></Example>
##  </Description>
##  </ManSection>
##  <#/GAPDoc>
